title: The Cat's Meow soundtrack
description:
Out of print soundtrack to the 2001 Bogdanovich film "The Cat&#039;s Meow," starring Kirsten Dunst as Marion Davies, Eddie Izzard as Charlie Chaplin, and Edward Herrmann as William Randolph Hearst.  A mix of authentic 1920&#039;s period tracks (Al Jolson, Paul Whiteman&#039;s Charleston) and modern recordings of period songs.  A must have for 20&#039;s music enthusiasts.

CD is currently unavailable from most sellers, though some copies are available from second-hand sources.
